						<summary>

						<p>Two Slabs built into a wall in the east <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of the Anantēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>This damaged and undated record registers gifts of land to the temple of Baḷamañjadēva for worship and feeding Brāhmaṇas. It mentions Tāyaṇa.</p>						

